<html>
<body>
<table border="0" align="center" width="700">
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding: 5px 0px;color: #999;font-size:0.9em;font-style:italic;">This email is intended for Human Resources. Please forward if necessary.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="border: 1px solid #ccc;padding:15px 30px;">
        <p align="center" style="margin: 0px">
          <%=link_to(image_tag("compsage_logo_email.gif", :size=> "200x47", :alt=>"CompSage", :border=>0), root_path(:only_path => false, :subdomain => subdomain_for(:email => @invitation.email))) %>
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top: 5px">
        Your organization has been invited by <%=@invitation.inviter.name%> to join CompSage! Joining now will give your
        colleague the ability to quickly and easily notify you of new surveys to participate in.
        </p>
        <p>CompSage is a tool to create online customized compensation surveys. Joining CompSage comes with a variety of
        benefits. You can:
          <ul>  
            <li>Design surveys using our standard questions or add questions of your own design.</li>
            <li>Participate in a survey and get results for free.</li>
            <li>Sponsor a survey for free and get great data that won't put you over-budget.</li>
            <li>Survey turnaround in as few as 3 days.</li>
            <li>Get guaranteed results, or you pay nothing.</li>
            <li>Access compensation data in use right now by the companies of your choosing.</li>
          </ul>  
        </p>
        <p>
          Becoming a member of CompSage is easy and free! To get started, please <%=link_to "click here", new_account_path(:key => @invitation.key, :only_path => false, :subdomain => subdomain_for(:email => @invitation.email))%>.
        </p>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>      
      <td align="Center">
        <a href="http://www.mfrall.com"><%= image_tag("MAG-LOGO-for-Print.png", :size=> "297x57", :alt=>"Manufacturers Alliance", :border=>0) %></a>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td align="Center" style="padding: 0px 0px; color: #999;font-size: 0.9em">CompSage is a service offered by Manufacturers Alliance.
      </td>
    </tr>    
